# Types of Networks

**LAN (Local Area Network)** connects local devices together.  
**WAN (Wide Area Network)** connects LANs together and operates over the Internet.

---

## Questions and Answers

**1. What type of network a computer in local is connected to?**  
- ✅ LAN  
- WAN  
- Internet

**2. What type of network could connect the Holberton HQ office with the Holberton-Gandi space?**  
- ✅ WAN  
- LAN  
- Internet

**3. What network do you use when you browse www.google.com from your smartphone (not connected to Wi-Fi)?**  
- ✅ Internet  
- LAN  
- WAN

